<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٢٤٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">‌حُمَيْدٌ </a>، سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسًا </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«تَزَوَّجَ عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ عَوْفٍ عَلَى وَزْنِ نَوَاةٍ مِنْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٩٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ذَهَبٍ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> أَوْلِمْ وَلَوْ بِشَاةٍ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>